  <p>Critics said that giving nursing homes less incentive to fix faulty and dangerous practices before someone gets hurt. When I did an analysis to calculate the total of fines issued against nursing homes per quarter, we can identify how numbers started to decrease again after Trump's rollback of Obama era policies and regulations of the nursing home industry.</p>
